# Simple Addition Program

## Overview
This project includes a simple function that adds two integers. The program also provides a user interface for users to input values and see the result.

## Files
- `src/addition.cpp`: Contains the `add` function and user interface code.
- `tests/test_addition.cpp`: Test harness for the `add` function.

## How to Build and Run
Use the Makefile to build the program and tests. See commands below.

## Usage
After building, run `./main` to start the addition program. To run tests, execute `./test`.
